snippet.title: Philanthropist Pays For Channel Subscribers Service Dog
snippet.description:
A member of the community will have his service dog paid for in full, if we as a community can combined put either our own videos about service dogs and or even mirror this video. To reach the goal, we need channels totaling a combined 250,000 subscribers to take part. Please, if you do your own video, or mirror this, let me know and I will add you link in the description box below so we can show as a combined effort we have managed to do our little bit. 

And just to clarify, the video does not need to be watched by 250k people, we just need channels with a core base of subscribers which total 250k :)

Special thanx to the following channels who have mirrored this or done their own video :)

Service Dog Paws https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9eWVJP-przQ&ab_channel=ServiceDogPaws
